{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "第三回写袁承志在华山随穆人清等习武，内功、剑法渐成根基，又发现夏雪宜遗留的金蛇剑、秘籍和旧物。金蛇郎君的谜团开始牵入他的命运。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "崔叔叔没事，你放心。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "袁承志道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "安大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "安大娘微笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "安大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从腕上脱下一只金丝镯子，给他戴在腕上，轻轻一捏，金丝镯子便即收小，不再落下，笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "安大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "安大娘眼圈红了，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老人呵呵大笑，说道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老人道：",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "袁承志又要磕头，那老人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不让我瞧你的功夫，怎么教你啊？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老人道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "袁承志向画中人瞧了两眼，心道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟子一定用功。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "穆人清道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "指指哑巴道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "袁承志道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个我会，倪叔叔以前教过的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "袁承志不敢和师父赌气，笑着不动。穆人清道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鹞子翻身",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非抓住你不可。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "破玉拳",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "混元掌",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "混元掌",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "混元功",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "混元功",
      "tone": "陈述",
