      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 718
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木桑道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚说了这句话，忽然叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木桑道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小刀挑刮下，蛇锥的蛇腹上现出一个",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父，金蛇郎君是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 724
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你说金蛇郎君是为避仇而到这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 730
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "木桑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 732
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "穆人清道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 732
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木桑道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "木桑叹道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "穆人清道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木桑道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "木桑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 760,
      "line_end": 760
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木桑道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师伯，我成吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "承志道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 766,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "穆人清寻思：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 766,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "承志忙道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木桑道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洞里有许多古怪东西。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 804
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "木桑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 810,
      "line_end": 810
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "穆人清沉吟道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 810,
      "line_end": 810
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木桑道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "木桑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 814,
      "line_end": 814
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "字迹是用墨笔所写。信封中又有两个小封套，一个封套上写着",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 852,
      "line_end": 852
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "，一个封套上写着",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 852,
      "line_end": 852
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "葬我骸骨之法",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 858,
      "line_end": 858
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我好人做到底，索性照你的吩咐做吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 862,
      "line_end": 862
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "启盒之法",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 886,
      "line_end": 886
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木桑道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金蛇秘笈",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 916,
      "line_end": 916
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_sang_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木桑道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "木桑道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 924,
      "line_end": 924
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "千变万劫棋国手",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 940,
      "line_end": 940
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "李自成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "闯王",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 954,
      "line_end": 954
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "袁承志见是师父朋友，过去拜倒，口称：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 970,
      "line_end": 970
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那两人忙即跪下，连称：",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 972,
      "line_end": 972
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大家起来。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 974,
      "line_end": 974
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "承志道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 984,
      "line_end": 984
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "承志道：",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 994,
      "line_end": 994
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_ren_qing",
      "speaker_name": "穆人清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "穆人清道：",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 994,
      "line_end": 994
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "点子爪子硬？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1066,
      "line_end": 1066
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_xue_yi",
      "speaker_name": "夏雪宜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在这里啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1090,
      "line_end": 1090
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_xue_yi",
      "speaker_name": "夏雪宜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金蛇秘笈",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1092,
      "line_end": 1092
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咦，那人要逃！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1098,
      "line_end": 1098
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "随即又在秃子的尸身上重重踢了一脚，说道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1112,
      "line_end": 1112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "呀",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1118,
      "line_end": 1118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着眼露凶光，举起匕首，狞笑两声，说道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1122,
      "line_end": 1122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张春九大喜，又问一句：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1134,
      "line_end": 1134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他怎么死的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 1136,
      "line_end": 1136
    }
